## Troubleshooting commun

### Probl√®me: Application "OutOfSync"
```bash
# V√©rifier les diff√©rences
argocd app diff demo-app-dev

# Forcer le sync
argocd app sync demo-app-dev --force
```

### Probl√®me: Sync √©choue
```bash
# Voir les logs d√©taill√©s
argocd app get demo-app-dev

# Voir les √©v√©nements
kubectl get events -n dev --sort-by='.lastTimestamp'

# V√©rifier les manifests
argocd app manifests demo-app-dev
```

### Probl√®me: Webhook ne fonctionne pas
```bash
# V√©rifier les logs du serveur
kubectl logs -n argocd deployment/argocd-server | grep webhook

# Tester manuellement
curl -X POST https://$ARGOCD_SERVER/api/webhook \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"ref":"refs/heads/main"}'
```

