## Nettoyage

```bash
# Supprimer les applications
argocd app delete demo-app-dev --yes
argocd app delete demo-app-staging --yes
argocd app delete demo-app-production --yes

# Ou via kubectl
kubectl delete application demo-app-dev -n argocd
kubectl delete application demo-app-staging -n argocd
kubectl delete application demo-app-production -n argocd

# Supprimer l'ApplicationSet
kubectl delete applicationset demo-apps -n argocd

# Supprimer le projet
kubectl delete appproject demo-project -n argocd

# Supprimer les namespaces
kubectl delete namespace dev staging production

# D√©sinstaller ArgoCD
kubectl delete -n argocd -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj/argo-cd/stable/manifests/install.yaml
kubectl delete namespace argocd

# Supprimer le repository local
cd ..
rm -rf argocd-demo
```

